{"type": "article", "id": 62387, "title": "Apple TV+ 找电影人拍广告背书，德邦快递换了个新 Logo | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-26T06:34:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9431, "name": "影视"}, {"id": 412, "name": "流媒体"}, {"id": 106, "name": "创业"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 46103, "name": "德邦"}, {"id": 1437, "name": "腾讯"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190326134109ndZ7FwUigWybLz6k.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2181750547/4353669694467689\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>法国箱包品牌 Lancel 昨天宣布林允成为品牌大使，</strong></a>并且发布了 LANCEL X 林允中国限定系列，包含四款双方一同创作的手袋。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134205y4zXUVmCpdvD9ukh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODAxMjM2MA==&amp;mid=2652987896&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=98ebb5612b436f4eade97a8cdbad5eb2&amp;chksm=bd04f55f8a737c49e975da8f0a115b94dfa2177a751063a8c955edbe63019875ef70c7f28065&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=03260bSlmjtD4Y4cjYcxkbZV&amp;key=f1b1b4aaf75e0cb594a1703b9eaeead22a5c283ffa5bfde954b8218d32e12e7af51254d58f8b50ec273548dcc4b5d385f85ed41de1b49478cdf1a7a6b149f437434a5c68e5ad7786af6b57834d86c2d4&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=QdsxzLEICB2PZRVboKNbDeje2fzobFnbxFb%2FjjuWc7eyBSIvEYOLdDd72Q1Gpn5X\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>小程序京东购物圈启动“超级合伙人计划”，</strong></a>来孵化出更多的素人带货博主，京东会提供各种资源对这些潜在网红进行包装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134217k5W86MS40JKzDnOA.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134218H6KroVliztgEFLTU.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.327500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p><a href=\"https://fx.weico.net/share/64673395.html?weibo_id=4353705149184414\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>青岛啤酒和特步跨界推出 T 恤。</strong></a>设计上依然是将双方的品牌 Logo 融合在一起，加入啤酒元素。此外，顾客到特步天猫旗舰店定制相应图案，已经在线上做起限量预售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134250xCasLo6q1KHcQke3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.151899\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903261342506hbsTni0tM8dOfql.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.040506\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134250yGbKfevWRx5shuUV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.806329\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RrdbT4hpwBk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>苹果昨天宣布推出新内容服务，发布的 Apple TV+ 短片也是其中一部分。</strong></a>J·J·艾布拉姆斯等 10 位著名电影人出镜，五分多钟的片子讲述了他们的创作经历，既有焦虑也有愉悦。<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RrdbT4hpwBk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">此外，苹果稍晚还发布了自己出品的电视剧混剪预告。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=i08540he0a6\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=n0854a9i5q2\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p>Chanel 的合作对象第一次没有选择设计师，而是和音乐人 Pharrell 推出联名系列。<strong><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BvZXoK3hhwC/?utm_source=ig_embed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">并且拍摄了音乐电影来宣传新系列</a>，</strong>片中一群年轻人身着充满街头感的 Chanel 服饰在公路上旅行。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=i085427txfy\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BvZXoK3hhwC/?utm_source=ig_embed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">瑞幸和腾讯合作开了家咖啡店 “1999 beta”，表示是对当年腾讯创业的怀念</a>。</strong>消费者出示已登录的 5 位或者是 6 位 QQ 号可以免费获得一杯拿铁。咖啡店开业时间为期一个月（3 月 25 日—— 4 月 24 日），位于深圳市南山区航天科技广场裙楼一层。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134534uBkCfzYb6dINPr5t.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666902\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134534vSnKdQ70LYPazIBX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666902\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134534hQktK4RCaMBoVZ26.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.432275\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134534LPrYhVWTEBqcKv69.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.432275\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134535X4mlWDei9yxv0RNZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.396296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134534tYxGnh4vJmIaK5Xw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4353750112110948?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>德邦快递换了新 Logo。</strong></a>虽然还是原来的蓝黄配色，色调更加明亮了。德邦对新 Logo 的方形元素和交错排布如此解释，前者是化用了包裹的外形，而交错排布是为了宣传大件快递他们也会送上楼的服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134610iUSxd45cjJvpEX96.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326134610dmNClfDcMPbqn0U1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.460000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTc5MjkxNQ==&amp;mid=2247483896&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=643ff999d8594f6c1b6daf1bf3c798fb&amp;key=d2e42a84cf84ae844948fa93219cee088e6d78164805b5e6270063fd91974b3d39abf00894d547d1c8ed9aae666b5509c08b60960516e8b03a19a5540ed10194f5b474ea14f04470d79a37020c6a00a4&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=QdsxzLEICB2PZRVboKNbDeje2fzobFnbxFb%2FjjuWc7eyBSIvEYOLdDd72Q1Gpn5X\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>最近，哈啰顺风车发布了一支反复“哈哈哈哈哈”的广告。</strong></a>线上投放之外，也选择了电梯。15 秒的广告里面，每一句补贴活动之前，都用并不好笑的”哈哈哈哈哈“开头。品牌为了加强效果，配音还刻意展现出占到便宜的语气。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0848eer7rm\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/creative-works/project/atomic-london-i-newspaper-see-every-angle\" rel=\"nofollow\">i News 推出了一系列名人肖像海报 “'See Every Angle'”</a>，展示了来自政治、电影、体育和传媒的特朗普、特蕾莎·梅、扎克伯格等 9 位名人。旁边用三种不同颜色及描述来彰显，它要坚守公正性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326140655f5PBKwsAJrcoUXH3.png\" data-ratio=\"1.225806\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903261406561PxzJ7jfvu6p4XKo.png\" data-ratio=\"1.233387\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190326140656XMrW274KCjPtZSwz.png\" data-ratio=\"1.233871\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903261406573RmLBOJr4gjbKFc0.png\" data-ratio=\"1.228663\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自：Apple TV&nbsp;截图</p>"}